From 53cb66a053be27f59980f628126d9ccf89d19608 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Claude <noreply@anthropic.com>
Date: Sun, 19 Jul 2026 12:31:15 +0000
Subject: [PATCH] Redesign the whole site with an iOS-style look and kiosk
 ordering

- Add a real SVG logo (app-icon tile + slice glyph) to header/footer
- Rebuild the hero: centered composition with hand-drawn pizza art
  (pulled slice, scroll rotation, floating garnish); drop the
  text-left/placeholder-right layout and the bullet-point badges
- Replace the menu cards with kiosk-style ordering: segmented category
  control, product tiles with food illustrations, and an iOS bottom
  sheet for extras + quantity
- Shrink monthly offers into a compact horizontal card strip
- Rebuild the lucky wheel in SVG with a working spin (transitionend
  instead of a timeout) and a side-by-side result panel
- Add a Find Us section with an embedded map, tap-to-call and hours
- Checkout: "use my location" now reverse-geocodes and fills the
  address input; route preview renders inline under the input instead
  of opening a new tab; iOS grouped-form styling
- Move the shop to 37-5 Mosine Kokalari, Mitrovica e Veriut
  (42.874094, 20.858669)
- Trim overselling copy in both locales; add on-scroll reveal
  animations (reduced-motion aware); switch next/image priority to
  the Next 16 preload prop

Co-Authored-By: Claude Fable 5 <noreply@anthropic.com>
Claude-Session: https://claude.ai/code/session_01LQSh1phQBiMcrk6FKaJYeb
